truffaut ( french : les &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 1962 french drama film directed by françois truffaut and starring françois truffaut , françois truffaut and françois truffaut . the film is based on the 1962 french novel les &lt;unk&gt; de la nuit by françois truffaut . the film was selected as the french entry for the best foreign language film at the 68th academy awards , but was not accepted as a nominee . the film was selected for preservation in the united states national film registry by the library of congress as being " culturally , historically , or aesthetically significant " .